                            <p>This inscription is dated in the 17th year of the reign of the ancient <hi rend="bold">Chōḷa</hi> king <hi rend="bold">Rājakēsarivarman</hi>. It was meant to record some decision of the village assembly, but was left unfinished for unknown reasons.</p>						
                            
