            <div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:grantha maturity:vernacular">
                
                <p>
                    <lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <hi rend="grantha"><supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied> ko rājakesariva<unclear>r</unclear>mma</hi>ṟ<hi rend="grantha">ku</hi> yāṇṭu <num value="17"><g type="numeral">10</g> 7</num> Āvatu nāḷ <num value="122"><unclear>100</unclear> 2 <g type="numeral">10</g> 2</num> In=nāḷāl <hi rend="grantha">śrīvikramābharaṇaccatu<unclear>r</unclear><surplus>v</surplus>ve</hi><choice><sic>ti</sic><corr><hi rend="grantha">di</hi></corr></choice><hi rend="grantha">maṃ</hi>
                    <lb n="2" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha"><choice><sic>k</sic><corr>g</corr></choice>alattu</hi> Ivvāṭṭai <hi rend="grantha"><unclear>sa</unclear><choice><sic>M</sic><corr>ṁ</corr></choice>vatsaravāri</hi>yapperumakkaḷum E<choice><sic>k</sic><corr>r</corr></choice>ivāriyapperum<hi rend="grantha"><unclear>bha</unclear></hi>ṭṭarka<unclear>ḷu</unclear>m <hi rend="grantha">viśi</hi>
                    <lb n="3" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">ṣṭa</hi>rkaḷumuḷḷi<supplied reason="omitted">ṭṭa</supplied> <hi rend="grantha">mahāsabhai</hi>yom<unclear>m</unclear>e<supplied reason="omitted">m</supplied>mūr puvaṉimāṇikkavi<hi rend="grantha">ṣṇ<unclear>u</unclear>gṛha</hi>tte kūṭa Irun<hi rend="grantha">tu</hi> <gap reason="lost" quantity="25" unit="character"/> 
                </p>
                
            </div>
            
            <div type="apparatus">
                <listApp>
                    <app loc="1">
                        <lem><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi></lem>
                        <note>These two words are engraved to the left of lines 1 and 2.</note>
                    </app>
                </listApp>
            </div>
            
            <div type="translation" source="bib:Hultzsch1899_01">
                
                <p>Hail ! Prosperity ! On the 122nd day of the 17th year (<hi rend="italic">of the reign</hi>) of king <hi rend="bold">Rājakēsarivarman</hi>,—we, the great assembly of <hi rend="bold">Śrī-Vikramābharaṇa-chaturvēdimaṅgalam</hi>,—including the great men elected for this year, the great <hi rend="italic">Bhaṭṭas</hi> elected for (<hi rend="italic">the supervision of</hi>) the tank, and (<hi rend="italic">all other</hi>) distinguished men,—being assembled on this day in the <hi rend="bold">Puvaṉimāṇikka-Vishṇugṛiham</hi> in our village, . . . . . . . . . .</p>
                
            </div>
            
